Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:44.05,NEP,,0,0,0,,According to Yuukimaru,\NGuren the Crystal Style user is alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.35,0:22:48.28,NEP,,0,0,0,,And he says that Naruto and this Guren\Nwere swallowed by the Three-Tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:51.15,NEP,,0,0,0,,That story may have some truth to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:53.52,NEP,,0,0,0,,But how do you know that Guren is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:57.22,NEP,,0,0,0,,If something happens to Guren,\Nthis crystal will break, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:00.12,NEP,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't mean that Naruto is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:03.88,NEP,,0,0,0,,We need to believe he's still alive\Nand find the Three-Tails first.
